- rata ownership basis.","Profit Interests currently have no value but could have value if company earns sufficient cash flow or if future fundraising rounds are successful.",24143,107217,"12",{"description":235,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":89,"endnote":7,"entity_id":236,"id":237,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":29,"income_type":94,"line_no":238,"metadata":94,"value_category_id":111,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},"KalshiEx (US registered derivative exchange), unvested stock options",24144,107215,"13",{"description":240,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":89,"endnote":7,"entity_id":241,"id":242,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":29,"income_type":94,"line_no":243,"metadata":94,"value_category_id":95,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},"Next Level Derivatives, LLC, vested stock options (value not readily ascertainable): 10,000 vested shares, strike $25, vest 6/2023, exp. 1/2026",24145,107218,"14",{"description":147,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":126,"endnote":7,"entity_id":148,"id":245,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":11,"metadata":246,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},107232,"I will continue to participate in this defined contribution plan. The plan sponsor no longer makes contributions. (2023-01-01)",{"description":248,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":126,"endnote":7,"entity_id":249,"id":250,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":37,"metadata":251,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},"CNK Equity Partners III, LLC, AH Capital Management",6969,107227,"I hold vested and unvested carried interests in CNK Fund III LP, and an interest in the fund’s general partner, CNK Equity Partners III, LLC. These interests were received as compensation for my services provided to AH Capital Management as of December 2021. The percentage of my carried interest was fixed as of the grant date and payment will be made if and when the fund profits from its investments. AH Capital Management has agreed to accelerate the vesting of my unvested carried interest at the time of my separation. This will occur prior to me assuming the duties of the position of Chairman.  I will divest my full carried interest in CNK Fund III, LP and my interest in CNK Equity Partners III, LLC prior to assuming the duties of the position of Chairman. (2021-12-01)",{"description":253,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":126,"endnote":7,"entity_id":254,"id":255,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":43,"metadata":256,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},"CNK Equity Partners Seed I, LLC, AH Capital Management",6970,107230,"I hold vested and unvested carried interests in CNK Seed 1 Fund, and an interest in the fund’s general partner, CNK Equity Partners Seed I, LLC. These interests were received as compensation for my services provided to AH Capital Management as of July 2022. The percentage of my carried interest was fixed as of the grant date and payment will be made if and when the fund profits from its investments.  AH Capital Management has agreed to accelerate the vesting of my unvested carried interest at the time of my separation. This will occur prior to me assuming the duties of the position of Chairman.  I will divest my full carried interest in CNK Seed 1 Fund and my interest in CNK Equity Partners Seed I, LLC prior to assuming the duties of the position of Chairman. (2022-07-01)",{"description":258,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":126,"endnote":7,"entity_id":259,"id":260,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":49,"metadata":261,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},"CNK Equity Partners IV, LLC, AH Capital Management",6971,107228,"I hold vested and unvested carried interests in CNK IV Fund LP, and an interest in the fund’s general partner, CNK Equity Partners IV, LLC. These interests were received as compensation for my services provided to AH Capital Management as of July 2022.  The percentage of my carried interest was fixed as of the grant date and payment will be made if and when the fund profits from its investments.  AH Capital Management has agreed to accelerate the vesting of my unvested carried interest at the time of my separation. This will occur prior to me assuming the duties of the position of Chairman.  I will divest my full carried interest in CNK IV Fund LP and my interest in CNK Equity Partners IV LLC prior to assuming the duties of the position of Chairman. (2022-07-01)",{"description":253,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":126,"endnote":7,"entity_id":254,"id":263,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":55,"metadata":264,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},107231,"I hold vested and unvested carried interests in CNK Seed 1 Fund, and an interest in the fund’s general partner, CNK Equity Partners Seed I, LLC. These interests were received as compensation for my services provided to AH Capital Management as of March 2023. The percentage of my carried interest was fixed as of the grant date and payment will be made if and when the fund profits from its investments.  AH Capital Management has agreed to accelerate the vesting of my unvested carried interest at the time of my separation. This will occur prior to me assuming the duties of the position of Chairman.  I will divest my full carried interest in CNK Seed 1 Fund and my interest in CNK Equity Partners Seed I, LLC prior to assuming the duties of the position of Chairman. (2023-03-01)",{"description":258,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":126,"endnote":7,"entity_id":259,"id":266,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":61,"metadata":267,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},107229,"I hold vested and unvested carried interests in CNK IV Fund LP, and an interest in the fund’s general partner, CNK Equity Partners IV, LLC. These interests were received as compensation for my services provided to AH Capital Management as of March 2023. The percentage of my carried interest was fixed as of the grant date and payment will be made if and when the fund profits from its investments.  AH Capital Management has agreed to accelerate the vesting of my unvested carried interest at the time of my separation. This will occur prior to me assuming the duties of the position of Chairman.  I will divest my full carried interest in CNK IV Fund LP and my interest in CNK Equity Partners IV LLC prior to assuming the duties of the position of Chairman. (2023-03-01)",{"description":269,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":126,"endnote":7,"entity_id":270,"id":271,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":66,"metadata":272,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},"Next Level Derivatives LLC (market research company)",6972,107234,"I was granted a profit interest in Next Level Derivatives for services provided as of January 2022. The terms of that profit interest were fixed as of January 2022. I will divest my full profit interest and any vested stock options prior to assuming the duties of the position of Chairman. (2022-01-01)",{"description":34,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":126,"endnote":7,"entity_id":35,"id":274,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":72,"metadata":275,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},107233,"I receive stock options as compensation for my service as a Director, which vest on a monthly basis.  Upon entering into government service, I will divest of all of my stock and any vested options, and I will forfeit any unvested options. (2021-11-01)",{"description":27,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":277,"endnote":7,"entity_id":30,"id":278,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":11,"metadata":279,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},4,107235,"Services as Global Head of Policy, Crypto",{"description":52,"appointee_id":28,"dsid":277,"en